{"tid":1898311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 可以點樣幫返韓國手足","createTime":"2020-02-26T04:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T04:21:00.000Z","uid":81268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3477e7ba4acb183fa66cb02721a139b10f255b79","tid":1898311,"uid":81268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:50:36.000Z","msg":"今日韓國感染人數已經破千，社區傳播已經失控，港共直頭對韓國封埋關<br />\n<br />\n有冇身處韓國嘅手足可以講下而家嗰邊實際情況係點？口罩同其他消毒用品缺唔缺？市民防疫意識有冇提高？<br />\n<br />\n成個反送中以來韓國人一直咁撐我哋，而家係時候做啲嘢幫返人地<br />\n<br />\n出錢出力出物資出資訊乜都好，我哋應該諗下點樣幫返佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">呢半年來韓仔咁撐我地 要點答謝人地?</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747990</a></span>"},{"pid":"6775fb73bb4728454a6a4061d0d3246db181ab60","tid":1898311,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"1萬蚊捐d過去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f448c51467c8ecd86b52f619b79d971ff32e7384","tid":1898311,"uid":84064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe7a3239d79555edf2eb483dc400362013f3b760","tid":1898311,"uid":148262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"push"}]}